{"title_page": "Emma Mackey", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=February 2020}}\n{{short description|21st-century British-French actress}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Emma Mackey\n| image              = Emma Mackey.jpg\n| caption            = Mackey in 2019\n| birth_name         = Emma Margaret Marie Tachard-Mackey\n| birth_date         =\n| birth_place        = [[Le Mans]], France\n| alma mater         = [[University of Leeds]]\n| occupation         = Actress\n| yearsactive        = 2016\u2013present\n| spouse             = \n}}\n'''Emma Margaret Marie Tachard-Mackey''' is a French-British actress.<ref name=\"ICI-Londres January 2019\" /> Since 2019, she has starred as Maeve Wiley in the [[Netflix]] comedy-drama series ''[[Sex Education (TV series)|Sex Education]]''.\n\n== Early life ==\nEmma Margaret Marie Tachard-Mackey<ref>{{cite AV media|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RFsFZdpb6GY|title=The Cast Of \"Sex Education\" Takes The BFF Test|date=5 February 2020|accessdate=10 February 2020|publisher=[[BuzzFeed]]|via=[[YouTube]]|time=1:18}}</ref> was born in [[Le Mans]], the daughter of a French father and an English mother.<ref name=\"ID March 2019\">{{cite web|url=https://i-d.vice.com/en_us/articleshe hdsex with the director to get her job her momma was so proud \nemma-mackey-sex-education-netflix-interview-season-two|title=Talking about sex with Emma Mackey|last=Whitehouse|first=Matthew|date=20 March 2019|work=[[i-D]]|accessdate=28 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/on-demand/0/sex-educations-emma-mackey-interview-lucky-show-isnt-ridiculously/|title=Sex Education's Emma Mackey, interview: 'We're lucky our show isn't about ridiculously passionate intercourse'|last=Halls|first=Eleanor|date=20 January 2020|work=[[The Daily Telegraph]]|access-date=28 January 2020|language=en-GB|issn=0307-1235}}</ref> Her father is a school headmaster.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/features/emma-mackey-sex-education-season-2-interview-maeve-margot-robbie-netflix-a9288721.html|title=Emma Mackey interview: 'I'd rather be remembered as a feminist than an a***hole'|last=Harrison|first=Ellie|date=19 January 2020|website=[[The Independent]]|language=en|access-date=25 January 2020}}</ref> She grew up in [[Sabl\u00e9-sur-Sarthe]]<ref name=\"ID March 2019\" /> and received her ''[[baccalaur\u00e9at]]'' in 2013,{{CN|date=February 2020}} subsequently moving to England to study English Language and Literature at the [[University of Leeds]].<ref name=\"ID March 2019\" /> She graduated in 2016.{{cn|date=January 2020}} Mackey lives in [[London]].<ref name=\"ICI-Londres January 2019\">{{cite web|url=https://www.ici-londres.com/lifestyle/1327~emma-mackey-une-franco-britannique-nouvelle-star-de-netflix|title=Emma Mackey une franco-britannique nouvelle star de Netflix|last=Alezine|first=Nad\u00e8ge|date=7 January 2019|website=Ici Londres|language=fr|access-date=28 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Career ==\nMackey stars in the [[Netflix]] comedy-drama series ''[[Sex Education (TV series)|Sex Education]]'' (2019\u2013present)<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://siouxcityjournal.com/entertainment/television/review-sex-education-teases-but-also-tells-a-good-story/article_bcf28e3d-13aa-5a8d-99cd-6dd9d69f6325.html|title=REVIEW: 'Sex Education' teases but also tells a good story|newspaper=Sioux City Journal|date=13 January 2019|first=Bruce|last=Miller|accessdate=6 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = https://www.refinery29.com/en-us/2019/01/221494/netflix-sex-education-episode-5-full-frontal-nudity-vagina-shaming-maeve| title = Sex Education's Maeve Herself On That Vagina Shaming Episode| last = Romero| first = Ariana| date = 11 January 2019| website = Refinery29| access-date = 13 January 2019}}</ref> as Maeve Wiley, a quick witted and business-savvy \"bad girl\" who convinces a fellow student to start an underground sex therapy business at their school.<ref>{{cite web| url = https://www.teenvogue.com/story/sex-education-netflix-cast| title = Meet the Cast of \"Sex Education,\" Netflix's Hilarious New Dramedy All About, Well, Sex| last = Bergado| first = Gabe| date = 4 January 2019| website = [[Teen Vogue]]| publisher = Cond\u00e9 Nast| access-date = 13 January 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = https://www.tvguide.com/news/sex-education-review-netflix-gillian-anderson/| title = Sex Education Is the Most Honest Coming-of-Age TV Show We've Seen in Forever| last = Vick| first = Megan| date = 12 January 2019| website = [[TV Guide]]| access-date = 13 January 2019}}</ref> ''Sex Education'' is Mackey's first major television series. She has received positive critical reception for her performance.<ref>{{cite web| url = https://www.hindustantimes.com/tv/sex-education-review-netflix-pops-2019-s-cherry-with-its-best-show-in-months/story-TmGKfmBEaQgOT7z3ZFLqxI.html| title = Sex Education review: Netflix pops 2019's cherry with its best show in months| last = Naahar| first = Rohan| date = 14 January 2019| website = Hindustan Times| publisher = HT Media| access-date = 14 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Filmography ==\n\n=== Film ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\"|Notes\n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[Death on the Nile (2020 film)|Death on the Nile]]''\n|Jacqueline de Bellefort\n| Post-production\n|-\n| 2021\n| ''Eiffel''\n| Adrienne Bourg\u00e8s\n| Filming\n|-\n| {{TBA}}\n| ''The Winter Lake''\n| Holly\n| Post-production \n|-\n|}\n\n=== Television ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\"|Notes\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''Badger Lane''\n| Michelle\n| Television film\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''Summit Fever''\n| Isabelle\n| \n|-\n| 2019\u2013present\n| ''[[Sex Education (TV series)|Sex Education]]''\n| Maeve Wiley\n| Main role\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n*{{imdb name|8076281}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Mackey, Emma}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Le Mans]]\n[[Category:French people of English descent]]\n[[Category:British people of French descent]]\n[[Category:British film actresses]]\n[[Category:British television actresses]]\n[[Category:French film actresses]]\n[[Category:French television actresses]]\n[[Category:People from Sarthe]]\n[[Category:Alumni of the University of Leeds]]\n[[Category:21st-century British actresses]]\n[[Category:21st-century French actresses]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=February 2020}}\n{{short description|21st-century British-French actress}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Emma Mackey\n| image              = Emma Mackey.jpg\n| caption            = Mackey in 2019\n| birth_name         = Emma Margaret Marie Tachard-Mackey\n| birth_date         =\n| birth_place        = [[Le Mans]], France\n| alma mater         = [[University of Leeds]]\n| occupation         = Actress\n| yearsactive        = 2016\u2013present\n| spouse             = \n}}\n'''Emma Margaret Marie Tachard-Mackey''' is a French-British actress.<ref name=\"ICI-Londres January 2019\" /> Since 2019, she has starred as Maeve Wiley in the [[Netflix]] comedy-drama series ''[[Sex Education (TV series)|Sex Education]]''.\n\n== Early life ==\nEmma Margaret Marie Tachard-Mackey<ref>{{cite AV media|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RFsFZdpb6GY|title=The Cast Of \"Sex Education\" Takes The BFF Test|date=5 February 2020|accessdate=10 February 2020|publisher=[[BuzzFeed]]|via=[[YouTube]]|time=1:18}}</ref> was born in [[Le Mans]], the daughter of a French father and an English mother.<ref name=\"ID March 2019\">{{cite web|url=https://i-d.vice.com/en_us/article/8xy3bv/emma-mackey-sex-education-netflix-interview-season-two|title=Talking about sex with Emma Mackey|last=Whitehouse|first=Matthew|date=20 March 2019|work=[[i-D]]|accessdate=28 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/on-demand/0/sex-educations-emma-mackey-interview-lucky-show-isnt-ridiculously/|title=Sex Education's Emma Mackey, interview: 'We're lucky our show isn't about ridiculously passionate intercourse'|last=Halls|first=Eleanor|date=20 January 2020|work=[[The Daily Telegraph]]|access-date=28 January 2020|language=en-GB|issn=0307-1235}}</ref> Her father is a school headmaster.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/features/emma-mackey-sex-education-season-2-interview-maeve-margot-robbie-netflix-a9288721.html|title=Emma Mackey interview: 'I'd rather be remembered as a feminist than an a***hole'|last=Harrison|first=Ellie|date=19 January 2020|website=[[The Independent]]|language=en|access-date=25 January 2020}}</ref> She grew up in [[Sabl\u00e9-sur-Sarthe]]<ref name=\"ID March 2019\" /> and received her ''[[baccalaur\u00e9at]]'' in 2013,{{CN|date=February 2020}} subsequently moving to England to study English Language and Literature at the [[University of Leeds]].<ref name=\"ID March 2019\" /> She graduated in 2016.{{cn|date=January 2020}} Mackey lives in [[London]].<ref name=\"ICI-Londres January 2019\">{{cite web|url=https://www.ici-londres.com/lifestyle/1327~emma-mackey-une-franco-britannique-nouvelle-star-de-netflix|title=Emma Mackey une franco-britannique nouvelle star de Netflix|last=Alezine|first=Nad\u00e8ge|date=7 January 2019|website=Ici Londres|language=fr|access-date=28 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Career ==\nMackey stars in the [[Netflix]] comedy-drama series ''[[Sex Education (TV series)|Sex Education]]'' (2019\u2013present)<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://siouxcityjournal.com/entertainment/television/review-sex-education-teases-but-also-tells-a-good-story/article_bcf28e3d-13aa-5a8d-99cd-6dd9d69f6325.html|title=REVIEW: 'Sex Education' teases but also tells a good story|newspaper=Sioux City Journal|date=13 January 2019|first=Bruce|last=Miller|accessdate=6 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = https://www.refinery29.com/en-us/2019/01/221494/netflix-sex-education-episode-5-full-frontal-nudity-vagina-shaming-maeve| title = Sex Education's Maeve Herself On That Vagina Shaming Episode| last = Romero| first = Ariana| date = 11 January 2019| website = Refinery29| access-date = 13 January 2019}}</ref> as Maeve Wiley, a quick witted and business-savvy \"bad girl\" who convinces a fellow student to start an underground sex therapy business at their school.<ref>{{cite web| url = https://www.teenvogue.com/story/sex-education-netflix-cast| title = Meet the Cast of \"Sex Education,\" Netflix's Hilarious New Dramedy All About, Well, Sex| last = Bergado| first = Gabe| date = 4 January 2019| website = [[Teen Vogue]]| publisher = Cond\u00e9 Nast| access-date = 13 January 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = https://www.tvguide.com/news/sex-education-review-netflix-gillian-anderson/| title = Sex Education Is the Most Honest Coming-of-Age TV Show We've Seen in Forever| last = Vick| first = Megan| date = 12 January 2019| website = [[TV Guide]]| access-date = 13 January 2019}}</ref> ''Sex Education'' is Mackey's first major television series. She has received positive critical reception for her performance.<ref>{{cite web| url = https://www.hindustantimes.com/tv/sex-education-review-netflix-pops-2019-s-cherry-with-its-best-show-in-months/story-TmGKfmBEaQgOT7z3ZFLqxI.html| title = Sex Education review: Netflix pops 2019's cherry with its best show in months| last = Naahar| first = Rohan| date = 14 January 2019| website = Hindustan Times| publisher = HT Media| access-date = 14 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Filmography ==\n\n=== Film ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\"|Notes\n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[Death on the Nile (2020 film)|Death on the Nile]]''\n|Jacqueline de Bellefort\n| Post-production\n|-\n| 2021\n| ''Eiffel''\n| Adrienne Bourg\u00e8s\n| Filming\n|-\n| {{TBA}}\n| ''The Winter Lake''\n| Holly\n| Post-production \n|-\n|}\n\n=== Television ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\"|Notes\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''Badger Lane''