ins Bayern Munich in a three-year deal\"/>\n|-\n| 5\n| DF\n| {{flagicon|MAR}} Medhi Benatia\n| 27\n| No\n| Transfer\n| Five years\n| 30 June 2019\n| \n| <ref name=\"Transfer von Benatia ist fix\"/>\n|-\n| 3\n| MF\n| {{flagicon|ESP}} Xabi Alonso\n| 32\n| Yes\n| Transfer\n| Two years\n| 30 June 2016\n| \n| <ref name=\"Xabi Alonso gegen Schalke schon im Bayern-Kader\"/>\n|-\n| 24\n| FW\n| {{flagicon|GER}} Sinan Kurt\n| 17\n| Yes\n| Transfer\n| Four years\n| 30 June 2018\n| \n| <ref name=\"Einigung erzielt: Gladbachs Kurt wechselt zum FC Bayern\"/>\n|-\n| 16\n| MF\n| {{flagicon|GER}} [[Gianluca Gaudino]]\n| 18\n| Yes\n| First pro contract\n| Four years\n| 30 June 2018\n| \n| <ref name=\"Gianluca Gaudino nun Profi - Starke verl\u00e4ngert\">{{cite news|title=Gianluca Gaudino nun Profi - Starke verl\u00e4ngert|url=http://www.augsburger-allgemeine.de/sport/fussball/bundesliga/Gianluca-Gaudino-nun-Profi-Starke-verlaengert-id32365217.html|accessdate=17 December 2014|publisher=[[Augsburger Allgemeine]]|date=17 December 2014|language=German}}</ref>\n|-\n| 22\n| GK\n| {{flagicon|GER}} [[Tom Starke]]\n| 33\n| Yes\n| Extension\n| One year\n| 30 June 2016\n| \n| <ref name=\"Gianluca Gaudino nun Profi - Starke verl\u00e4ngert\"/>\n|-\n| \u2014\n| MF\n| {{flagicon|GER}} [[Joshua Kimmich]]\n| 19\n| Yes\n| Signing\n| Five years\n| 30 June 2020\n| Signed for the [[2015\u201316 FC Bayern Munich season|2015\u201316 season]].\n| <ref name=\"FC Bayern verpflichtet Joshua Kimmich\">{{cite news|title=FC Bayern verpflichtet Joshua Kimmich|url=http://www.sueddeutsche.de/sport/transfer-in-der-bundesliga-fc-bayern-verpflichtet-joshua-kimmich-1.2289583|accessdate=9 January 2015|publisher=S\u00fcddeutsche Zeitung|date=2 January 2015|language=German}}</ref>\n|-\n| 34\n| MF\n| {{flagicon|DEN}} [[Pierre-Emile H\u00f8jbjerg]]\n| 19\n| Yes\n| Extension\n| Three years\n| 30 June 2018\n| \n| <ref name=\"Hojbjerg-Leihe best\u00e4tigt - Vertrag verl\u00e4ngert!\">{{cite news|title=Hojbjerg-Leihe best\u00e4tigt - Vertrag verl\u00e4ngert!|url=http://www.abendzeitung-muenchen.de/inhalt.fc-bayern-muenchen-hojbjerg-leihe-bestaetigt-vertrag-verlaengert.60e4b756-5448-4d07-aa4e-0228d0afd6e8.html|accessdate=9 January 2015|publisher=[[Abendzeitung]]|date=8 January 2015|language=German}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Friendly results===\n{{legend2|#CCFFCC|Win|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend2|#FFFFCC|Draw|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend2|#FFCCCC|Loss|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" Style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Match\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Date<br>Kick-off<ref group=n name=time>Times up until 25 October 2014 are in [[Central European Summer Time|CEST]] ([[UTC+02:00]]). Times from 26 October 2014 to 28 March 2015 are in [[Central European Time|CET]] ([[UTC+01:00]]). Times on and after 29 March 2015 are in [[Central European Summer Time|CEST]] ([[UTC+02:00]]).</ref>\n! rowspan=\"2\" | {{Abbr|H/A/N|Home, away, or neutral venue}}\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Opponent\n! rowspan=\"2\" | {{Abbr|Res.|Results}}<br>{{Abbr|F\u2013A|Goals for\u2013goals against}}\n! rowspan=\"2\" | {{Abbr|Att.|Attendance}}\n! colspan=\"2\" | Goalscorers and disciplined players\n! rowspan=\"2\" | {{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n! style=\"width:180px\" | [[FC Bayern Munich|Bayern Munich]]\n! style=\"width:180px\" | Opponent\n|- style=\"background:#cfc\"\n| Dream Game\n| 18 July<br>18:00\n| [[Memminger Arena|N]]\n| Red Baroons Dietmannsried\n| 3\u20130\n| 11,150\n| [[David Alaba|Alaba]] {{goal|5||37}}<br>[[Daniel H\u00e4gler|H\u00e4gler]] {{goal|14}}\n| \u2014\n| <ref name=\"Bayern siegt bei Badstuber-Comeback\"/>\n|- style=\"background:#ffc\"\n| [[Exhibition game|Friendly]]\n| 21 July<br>18:30\n| [[MSV-Arena|A]]\n| [[MSV Duisburg]]\n| 1\u20131\n| 24,126\n| [[Robert Lewandowski|Lewandowski]] {{goal|62}}<br>[[Phillipp Steinhart|Steinhart]] {{yel|80}}\n| [[Fabian Schnellhardt|Schnellhardt]] {{goal|69}}\n| <ref name=\"Ein Treffer zum Einstand\"/>\n|- style=\"background:#ffc\"\n| rowspan=\"