9.2014, Vorrunde Gruppe E)|url=http://liveticker.sueddeutsche.de/fussball/champions-league/bayern-muenchen/manchester-city/2014-09-17.html|publisher=S\u00fcddeutsche Zeitung|accessdate=30 September 2014|language=German|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006085322/http://liveticker.sueddeutsche.de/fussball/champions-league/bayern-muenchen/manchester-city/2014-09-17.html|archive-date=6 October 2014|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#cfc\"\n| [[2014\u201315 UEFA Champions League group stage#CSKA Moscow v Bayern Munich|2]]\n| 30 September<br>18:00\n| [[Arena Khimki|A]]\n| [[PFC CSKA Moscow|CSKA Moscow]]\n| 1\u20130\n| 0\n| [[Thomas M\u00fcller|M\u00fcller]] {{goal|22|pen.}}<br>[[Philipp Lahm|Lahm]] {{yel|40}}<br>[[Medhi Benatia|Benatia]] {{yel|68}}\n| [[Roman Eremenko|Eremenko]] {{yel|45}}\n| 1\n| 6\n| <ref name=uclmd2>{{cite news|title=G\u00f6tze wird gelegt und M\u00fcller macht die 100 voll|url=http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/chleague/spielrunde/champions-league/2014-15/2/2798646/spielbericht_zska-moskau-1572_bayern-muenchen-14.html|accessdate=30 September 2014|newspaper=kicker|date=30 September 2014|language=German}}</ref><br><ref name=uclmd2t>{{cite web|title=Champions League - Spieltag / Tabelle|url=http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/chleague/spielrunde/champions-league/2014-15/2/3310/spieltag.html|website=kicker.de|publisher=kicker|accessdate=30 September 2014|language=German}}</ref><br><ref>{{cite web|title=ZSKA Moskau - Bayern M\u00fcnchen live (30.09.2014, Vorrunde Gruppe E)|url=http://liveticker.sueddeutsche.de/fussball/champions-league/zska-moskau/bayern-muenchen/2014-09-30.html|publisher=S\u00fcddeutsche Zeitung|accessdate=30 September 2014|language=German|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140929080649/http://liveticker.sueddeutsche.de//fussball/champions-league/zska-moskau/bayern-muenchen/2014-09-30.html|archive-date=29 September 2014|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#cfc\"\n| [[2014\u201315 UEFA Champions Le