bert sich zum ersten Titel\"/>\n|- style=\"background:#cfc\"\n| Audi Football Summit\n| 1 August<br>02:00\n| [[Red Bull Arena (New Jersey)|N]]\n| [[C.D. Guadalajara|Guadalajara]]\n| 1\u20130\n| 25,073\n| [[Claudio Pizarro|Pizarro]] {{goal|10}}<br>[[Javi Mart\u00ednez|Mart\u00ednez]] {{yel|28}}<br>[[Rafinha (footballer, born 1985)|Rafinha]] {{yel|87}}\n| [[Jair Pereira|Pereira]] {{yel|22}}<br>[[Jes\u00fas S\u00e1nchez Garc\u00eda|S\u00e1nchez]] {{yel|73}}<br>[[\u00c9dgar Sol\u00eds|Sol\u00eds]] {{yel|84}}\n| <ref name=\"GUADALAJARA VS. BAYERN M\u00dcNCHEN 0 - 1\"/>\n|- style=\"background:#fcc\"\n| [[2014 MLS All-Star Game]]\n| 7 August<br>03:55\n| [[Providence Park|A]]\n| [[2014 MLS All-Star Game#MLS All-Stars|MLS All-Stars]]\n| 1\u20132\n| 21,733\n| [[Robert Lewandowski|Lewandowski]] {{goal|8}}<br>[[J\u00e9r\u00f4me Boateng|Boateng]] {{yel|90+2}}\n| [[Bradley Wright-Phillips|Wright-Phillips]] {{goal|51}}<br>[[Osvaldo Alonso|Alonso]] {{yel|64}}<br>[[Landon Donovan|Donovan]] {{goal|70}}<br>[[Will Johnson (soccer)|Johnson]] {{yel|89}}\n| <ref name=\"MLS ALL STAR TEAM VS. BAYERN M\u00dcNCHEN 2 - 1\"/>\n|- style=\"background:#cfc\"\n| Paulaner Cup\n| 6 October<br>17:30\n| [[Sportpark Unterhaching|N]]\n| Paulaner Dream Team\n| 5\u20131\n| \u2014\n| [[Thomas M\u00fcller|M\u00fcller]] {{goal|36}}<br>[[Milos Pantovic|Pantovic]] {{goal|69}}<br>[[Michael Eberwein|Eberwein]] {{goal|75||79}}<br>[[Xabi Alonso|Alonso]] {{goal|85}}\n| [[Matthias Pr\u00fcnstner|Pr\u00fcnstner]] {{goal|71}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|title= Paulaner Cup yields goals and fun |url=https://www.fcbayern.de/us/matches/match-reports/2014/matchreport-paulaner-cup-2014-061014.php|accessdate=8 December 2014|date=6 October 2014|publisher=Bayern Munich}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#cfc\"\n| [[Exhibition game|Friendly]]\n| 13 January<br>18:05\n| [[Abdullah bin Khalifa Stadium|A]]\n| Qatar Stars League XI\n| 4\u20131\n| 6,838\n| [[Mitchell Weiser|Weiser]] {{goal|4||14}}<br>[[Franck Rib\u00e9ry|Rib\u00e9ry]] {{goal|43}}