igt Bayern im Alleingang|url=http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/chleague/spielrunde/champions-league/2014-15/9/2838539/spielbericht_bayern-muenchen-14_fc-barcelona.html|accessdate=12 May 2015|newspaper=kicker|date=12 May 2015|language=German}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Team record==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"| Competition\n!rowspan=\"2\"| First match\n!rowspan=\"2\"| Last match\n!rowspan=\"2\"| Starting round\n!rowspan=\"2\"| Final<br>position / round\n!colspan=\"9\"| Record\n|-\n!{{Abbr|M|Matches played}}\n!{{Abbr|W|Matches won}}\n!{{Abbr|D|Matches drawn}}\n!{{Abbr|L|Matches lost}}\n!{{Abbr|GF|Goals for}}\n!{{Abbr|GA|Goals against}}\n!{{Abbr|GD|Goal difference}}\n!{{Abbr|Win %|Winning percentage}}\n!{{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n| [[2014\u201315 Bundesliga|Bundesliga]]\n| 22 August\n| 23 May\n| \u2014\n| bgcolor=#ffd700 | Winners\n{{WDL|34|25|4|5|for=80|against=18|diff=yes}}\n| <ref name=md34t/>\n|-\n| [[2014\u201315 DFB-Pokal|DFB-Pokal]]\n| 17 August\n| 28 April\n| Round 1\n| Semifinals\n{{WDL|5|3|2|0|for=10|against=3|diff=yes}}\n| [[#DFB-Pokal results|DFB-Pokal results]]\n|-\n| [[2014 DFL-Supercup|DFL-Supercup]]\n| colspan=\"2\"| 13 August\n| Final\n| bgcolor=#C0C0C0| Runners-up\n{{WDL|1|0|0|1|for=0|against=2|diff=yes}}\n| <ref name=\"supercup\"/>\n|-\n| [[2014\u201315 UEFA Champions League|Champions League]]\n| 17 September\n| 12 May\n| Group stage\n| Semifinals\n{{WDL|12|8|1|3|for=33|against=13|diff=yes}}\n| [[#Group stage results|Group stage results]]<br>[[#Knockout phase results|Knockout phase results]]\n|-\n! colspan=\"5\"| Total\n{{WDLtot|52|36|7|9|for=123|against=36|diff=yes}}\n!\u2014\n|}\n\n==Player information==\n\n===Squad and statistics===\n\n====Squad, appearances, and goals scored====\n{{As of|2015|5|23}}\n{{Efs start|[[2014\u201315 Bundesliga|Bundesliga]]|[[2014\u201315 DFB-Pokal|DFB-Pokal]]|[[2014 DFL-Supercup|DFL-Supercup]]<ref name=\"supercup\"/>|[[2014\u201315 UEFA Champions League|Champions League]]}}\n{{Efs p