re-reduziert-boateng-fehlt-nur-noch-einmal.html|accessdate=9 February 2015|publisher=kicker|date=9 February 2015|language=German}}</ref>\n|-\n| 14 February\n| [[Hamburger SV]]\n|-\n| [[Xabi Alonso]]\n| 1\n| Red Card vs. [[FC Shakhtar Donetsk|Shakhtar Donetsk]]\n| UEFA Champions League\n| 11 March\n| Shakhtar Donetsk\n| <ref name=\"Bayern Munich awakening from winter-break hibernation\"/>\n|-\n| Xabi Alonso\n| 1\n| Fifth yellow card\n| Bundesliga\n| 14 March\n| [[SV Werder Bremen|Werder Bremen]]\n| <ref name=md24/>\n|-\n| Medhi Benatia\n| 1\n| Fifth yellow card\n| Bundesliga\n| 22 March\n| [[Borussia M\u00f6nchengladbach]]\n| <ref name=md26/>\n|-\n| [[Dante (footballer)|Dante]]\n| 1\n| Fifth yellow card\n| Bundesliga\n| 16 May\n| [[SC Freiburg]]\n| <ref name=\"Guardiola hat Wunschliste im Kopf\"/>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Pepe Reina]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2\n| rowspan=\"2\"| Red card vs. [[FC Augsburg]].\n| rowspan=\"2\"| Bundesliga\n| 16 May\n| SC Freiburg\n| rowspan=\"2\"| <ref name=\"Pepe Reina banned for two matches after Bayern Munich red card\"/>\n|-\n| 23 May\n| [[1. FSV Mainz 05|Mainz 05]]\n|}\n\n==Team kit==\n{|\n|{{Football kit\n| pattern_la = _bayern1415home\n| pattern_b  = _FCBAYERN_1415h\n| pattern_ra = _bayern1415home\n| pattern_sh = _adidaswhite\n| pattern_so = _FCBAYERN_1415h\n| leftarm = FFFFFF | body = FFFFFF| rightarm = FFFFFF | shorts = DD0000| socks = DD0000| title = Home}}\n|\n|{{Football kit\n| pattern_la = _bayern1415home\n| pattern_b  = _FCBAYERN_1415h\n| pattern_ra = _bayern1415home\n| pattern_sh = _adidaswhite\n| pattern_so = _FCBAYERN_1415h_short\n| leftarm = DD0000 | body = FFFFFF | rightarm = DD0000 | shorts = DD0000 | socks = DD0000 | title = Home alt.}}\n|\n|{{Football kit\n| pattern_la = _bayern1516h\n| pattern_b  = _bayern1516H\n| pattern_ra = _bayern1516h\n| pattern_sh = _bayern1516h\n| pattern_so = _bayern1516h\n| leftarm = FF0000 | body = FF0000 | rightarm = FF0000 | shorts = FF0000 | socks = FF0000 | title = Home 2}}\n|\n|{{Football 